  "message": "chore(gitignore,baselines): track benchmark baseline JSON files\n\nUpdate .gitignore to allow baselines/*.json while still ignoring other\nartifacts in baselines/. Add initial v0.1.0 benchmark baselines for\nFrankenRedis and Redis 7.2.4 across get, set, incr, mixed, and\npipeline16 workloads.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
